<h1>Plumbing</h1>

<ol type=1><p>

<li>Identify at least ten (10) parts of a common plumbing installation, and explain the uses of at least three.<p>

<li>Identify at least six (6) tools used in plumbing.<p>

<li>Show how to cut, thread, and connect water pipes.<p>

<li>Repair a leaking water closet.<p>

<li>Repair a faulty or leaking faucet.<p>

<li>Tell the correct way of reading a water meter, or tell how a simple water pump works.<p>

<li>Submit a sketch of, and explain the sewerage system in a house; or submit a sketch of, and explain how a septic tank works.<p>

<li>Enumerate two (2) local health regulations related to plumbing.</ol>

</span><p>    </td>
